## Remarks  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/includes/deprecatedcontent-md.md)]  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0b55e-102"><xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity>에서는 호스트 응용 프로그램의 상태를 설정할 수 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0b55e-102">The <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity> allows for setting the state from the host application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0b55e-103">상태를 설정하면 호스트 응용 프로그램에서 상태 시스템의 현재 상태를 재정의할 수 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0b55e-103">This enables the host application to override the current state of a state machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0b55e-104">이렇게 하려면 <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.SetStateEventArgs> 클래스의 인스턴스를 상수 <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity.SetStateQueueName?displayProperty=nameWithType>로 명명된 WorkflowQueue의 큐에 삽입합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0b55e-104">This can be accomplished by enqueuing an instance of the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.SetStateEventArgs> class to the WorkflowQueue named by the constant <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity.SetStateQueueName?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0b55e-105">이 작업을 더 간단하게 수행하려면 <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance.SetState%2A> 클래스에 <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance> 메서드를 사용합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0b55e-105">A simpler way to accomplish this is to use the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance.SetState%2A> method in the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance> class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0b55e-106"><xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance.SetState%2A> 메서드를 사용하여 호스트에서 SetState 작업을 수행하거나 다음 예제에서처럼 직접 이벤트를 상태 시스템 워크플로의 큐에 삽입하여 수행할 수 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0b55e-106">You can use the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance.SetState%2A> method to perform a SetState operation from the host, or you can do it yourself by enqueuing an event to the state machine workflow as shown in the following example.</span></span>  
  
```  
public void SetState(string targetStateName)  
{  
      if (targetStateName == null)  
      {  
            throw new ArgumentNullException("targetStateName");  
      }  
      SetStateEventArgs args1 = new SetStateEventArgs(targetStateName);  
      this.WorkflowInstance.EnqueueItemOnIdle("SetStateQueue", args1, null, null);  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0b55e-107">상태 시스템 워크플로에서는 `SetStateQueue`라고 하는 특수한 큐를 사용하여 이러한 특수한 이벤트를 수신 대기합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0b55e-107">The state machine workflow uses a special queue called `SetStateQueue` to listen to these special events.</span></span>
